Show HN: Tournacat – Sync Esports Schedules to Google Calendar Automatically
text:
Tournacat is simple a Google Calendar add-on that syncs Sync Esports schedules to Google Calendar automatically.

I built Tournacat out of the frustration of the lack of reliability of public calendar for Esports in general. Personally, I've been using this to make plans for watch party at my place weeks in advance.

Currently it supports Esports title like Dota 2, LoL, CS:GO, and Valorant. Down the road I'll look into adding more prominent Esports titles.

Show HN: Caption Meow – A Purrr-Fect Open-Source Social Network for Cat Lovers
text: Looking for a daily dose of creativity and laughter? Look no further than Caption Meow, the open source social network that challenges you to come up with the wittiest, funniest, and most purr-fect captions for our daily cat photos. Our community of cat lovers is always up for a good laugh, and with Caption Meow, you can vote for your favorite captions and compete with other users to see who can come up with the best one. Don't miss out on the hilarious cat-related content – sign up now and start your day with a smile right meow!
